<h3>freeScroll</h3>

<p>Enables content to be freely scrolled and flicked without aligning cells to an end position.</p>

<div class="example duo">
  <div class="example__code duo__cell">
    ``` js
    freeScroll: true
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="example__demo duo__cell">
    <div class="carousel" data-flickity='{ "freeScroll": true }'>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
    </div>
    {{> edit-demo default="bNLGNZ" }}
  </div>
</div>

<p>Enable <code>freeScroll</code> and <code>contain</code> for a simple horizontal scroller.</p>

<div class="example duo">
  <div class="example__code duo__cell">
    ``` js
    freeScroll: true,
    contain: true,
    // disable previous & next buttons and dots
    prevNextButtons: false,
    pageDots: false
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="example__demo duo__cell">
    <div class="carousel"
      data-flickity='{ "freeScroll": true, "contain": true, "prevNextButtons": false, "pageDots": false }'>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
    </div>
    {{> edit-demo default="zxRYGo" }}
  </div>
</div>

<p>Enable <code>freeScroll</code> and <code>wrapAround</code> and you can flick forever, man.</p>

<div class="example duo">
  <div class="example__code duo__cell">
    ``` js
    freeScroll: true,
    wrapAround: true
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="example__demo duo__cell">
    <div class="carousel" data-flickity='{ "freeScroll": true, "wrapAround": true }'>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
      <div class="carousel-cell"></div>
    </div>
    {{> edit-demo default="GgQRJX" }}
  </div>
</div>
